pters, there are factions against factions, a lot is going on and it's not told in a straight line often.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIt was strange because so much is confusing in this, but I feel a re-read would add a layer of commentary. The lead, the most soulful character, is mechanical which is so interesting. You really do ache for Mattie, she cares so much, and being caught between the rising tensions of a society you are totally drawn in. I guess this author may be Russian, which I totally get, it's very tragic and dramatic, haha.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eAgain, it's not an easy or quick read, and is not that uplifting, but there's a lovely artistry that was refreshing and compelled me to finish and lingered with me. Recommended for something different.","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/666892?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"steampunk","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/666892?shelf=steampunk"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/48605343"},"likeCount":15,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.h0715ktHIzQLb9xZhTJXOA":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.h0715ktHIzQLb9xZhTJXOA","__typename":"Contributor","works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":6}},"User:3042473":{"id":3042473,"__typename":"User","legacyId":3042473,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1260810531i/3042473._CR0,6,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":true,"textReviewsCount":89,"viewableName":"Sandy Parsons","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/3042473-sandy-parsons","contributor":{"__ref":"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.h0715ktHIzQLb9xZhTJXOA"},"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount